txt.en: 'Theres not much a hobbit can do in times likes these... is there?'
'I should have listened to father and never left Bucklebury.'
'Wonder if I can get on at a farm in Staddle? Maybe I can get out of this town.'
'Uncle Filbert is a very respectable hobbit, but he tends to be very... excitable.'
'My uncle is always complaining about one thing or another.'
